import './SubmitPage.css' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { findZipLocation } from '../scripts/zip-checker'; function SubmitPage({ data }) { const [location, setLocation] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { const zip_code = data["Zip Code"]; if (zip_code) { const locationData = findZipLocation(zip_code); if(locationData) { setLocation(locationData) } } }) // Assuming 'data' is an object with properties like 'region', 'stay', 'zipCode', etc. return (

Your Submission Details

Region: {data.Region || "N/A"}
Fly or not {data["Willing to fly?"] ? "Yes" : "No"}
Stay: {data.Stay || "N/A"}
Zip Code: {data["Zip Code"] || "N/A"}
Number of Guests: {data["Number of Guests"] || "N/A"}
Epic Pass: {data["Epic Pass"] ? "Yes" : "No"}
Ikon Pass: {data["Ikon Pass"] ? "Yes" : "No"}
Start Date: {data["Start Date"] || "N/A"}
End Date: {data["End Date"] || "N/A"}

Zip Code to Latitude/Longitude

{location && (

Latitude: {location.latitude}

Longitude: {location.longitude}

)}
); } export default SubmitPage;
